	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/2> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "See Walters and Johnson on the text of Livy 30.25.2. M. Servilium is corrected to L. Sergium from Polyb. 15.1.3 (Büttner-Wobst), and three 15th century Mss of Livy." .
